Governor █████ held a press conference █████ at which ██ accused
"out-of-state generators" of price gouging and market manipulation.  ██
called on ████ to expedite their investigation of the market and to provide
for consumer rebates if ████ cannot conclude that ██████████ prices are
"just and reasonable."

Below are my notes from the press conference.  Attached is the Governor's
press release.

